=== 票房 ===
北美方面，《紅雀》和《[[猛龍怪客_(2018年電影)|猛龍怪客]]》同天上映並競爭，外界預估《紅雀》在首週末能從3050間戲院中獲得2000萬至2400萬美元的票房<ref>{{cite web|url=http://variety.com/2018/film/news/black-panther-record-box-office-second-weekend-1202705772/|title=Will ‘Black Panther’ See One of the Best Second Weekends Ever?|website=[[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]]|date=2018-02-20|author=Dave McNary|accessdate=2018-02-21|archive-date=2018-02-21|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6xOwrkZkj?url=http://variety.com/2018/film/news/black-panther-record-box-office-second-weekend-1202705772/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。它在第一天賺進了600萬美元（其中包括週四晚上首映的120萬美元），並在首週共獲得了1700萬美元的票房，位居當週票房排名第二。
[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]]分析，由於該片的預算約6900萬美元，加上勞倫斯的片酬高達1500萬至2000萬美元之間，所以該首週票房成績並不盡人意<ref name=opening>{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2018/03/jennifer-lawrence-red-sparrow-black-panther-death-wish-bruce-willis-box-office-1202308124/|title=‘Black Panther’ Busts Past Half Billion; ‘Red Sparrow’ Flies Low With $17M – Sunday AM B.O. Update|website=[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]]|date=2018-03-04|author=Anthony D'Alessandro|accessdate=2018-03-05|archive-date=2018-03-07|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6xjQeinGD?url=http://deadline.com/2018/03/jennifer-lawrence-red-sparrow-black-panther-death-wish-bruce-willis-box-office-1202308124/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

